</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/0xv317-hIU0" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/03/apple-wants-iphones-to-detect-car-crashes-auto-dial-999/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-wants-iphones-to-detect-car-crashes-auto-dial-999</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>TP-Link 雙 11 購物節限時優惠　 特價入手 Wi-Fi 6 / Wi-Fi Mesh 路由器</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/EeukFbe4G_A/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 03 Nov 2021 08:25:20 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[家居無線]]></category><category><![CDATA[買物情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[路由器]]></category><category><![CDATA[1111]]></category><category><![CDATA[TP-LINK]]></category><category><![CDATA[雙 11]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069130</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>去到 11 月初，相信大家都會記得一年一度的雙 11 購物節又快將來到了，各品牌都會趁此機會提供震撼優惠價，讓 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>去到 11 月初，相信大家都會記得一年一度的雙 11 購物節又快將來到了，各品牌都會趁此機會提供震撼優惠價，讓大家可以用抵玩價格入手心頭好。TP-Link 最近就宣佈了他們的雙 11 購物節限時優惠，讓大家可以折扣入手 Wi-Fi 6 或 Wi-Fi Mesh 路由器，最低更達 44 折！究竟有甚麼抵玩產品？就讓我們來看看。</p><h2>第一類：雙 11 特賣產品</h2><table style="width: 40.4167%; height: 394px;" width="361"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 50.411%;" width="145"><strong>型號</strong></td><td style="width: 15.5148%;" width="72"><strong>震撼價</strong></td><td style="width: 13.7795%;" width="72"><strong>原價</strong></td><td style="width: 17.0071%;" width="72"><strong>折扣率</strong></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50.411%;">Deco X90 (2-Pack)</td><td style="width: 15.5148%;">$3,098</td><td style="width: 13.7795%;">$3,998</td><td style="width: 17.0071%;">77 折</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50.411%;">Deco X68 (2-Pack)</td><td style="width: 15.5148%;">$1,998</td><td style="width: 13.7795%;">$2,438</td><td style="width: 17.0071%;">82 折</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50.411%;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Deco X20 (3-Pack)</spa