tyle="width: 17.0071%;">86 折</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="color: #ff0000;">*表內紅字為推介款式</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Archer-AX10_4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069144" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Archer-AX10_4-694x533.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="533" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Archer-AX10_4-694x533.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Archer-AX10_4-768x590.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Archer-AX10_4.jpg 806w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 TP-Link 雙 11 購物節提供了多件產品作限時優惠，當中最抵玩的就是這款 TP-Link Archer AX10 Wi-Fi 6 路由器。它設有 4 支外置天線，而且支援 802.11ax AX1500 雙頻方案。原價 $699 現以特價 61 折的 $429 發售，十分抵玩。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069145" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="428" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high-664x900.jpg 664w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high-768x1041.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high-1133x1536.jpg 1133w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Deco-M4_high.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 428px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果大家想入手 Wi-Fi Mesh 類產品但又預算不多，TP-Link 這款 Deco M4 就十分適合大家了，它採用直立式圓柱形白色設計，典雅漂亮而且散熱效果佳。而且體積細小擺位方便，十分適合香港家居使用，而且每隻均可作主 / 副機使用，今次優惠每隻原價 $499，以特惠價 7 折的 $349 發售，買兩、三隻回家使用，就可完成 Wi-Fi Mesh 佈局，十分方便又抵玩。</p><h2>第二類：Wi-Fi 特賣產品</h2><table style="width: 40.9889%; height: 333px;" width="360"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 50.4149%;" width="144"><strong>型號</strong></td><td sty