</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/EeukFbe4G_A" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/03/tp-link-1111-2021-promotions/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tp-link-1111-2021-promotions</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Netflix Games 正式登場，暫時只提供 5 款遊戲</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/nU42ZAQ5Y1s/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 03 Nov 2021 08:01:27 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活娛樂]]></category><category><![CDATA[Netflix]]></category><category><![CDATA[Netflix Games]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069371</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Netflix 早前傳出進軍遊戲市場，隨後也在波蘭進行了小範圍的測試。稍早前 Netflix 終於正式推出了  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Netflix 早前傳出進軍遊戲市場，隨後也在波蘭進行了小範圍的測試。稍早前 Netflix 終於正式推出了 Netflix Games 遊戲服務，但現時首批推出的只有五款遊戲可供選擇，所有 Netflix 訂閱用戶都可免費遊玩。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4-694x370.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4-694x370.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4-1280x683.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4-768x410.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4-1536x820.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/68882FDD-1954-4756-8B68-E628ACA76AF4.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Netflix Games 無需額外下載 App，在打開 Netflix 後，可看到一個新的遊戲選項卡，然後挑選你想要下載的遊戲。但目前 Netflix Games 僅在 Android 作業系統推出，iOS 則有待 Netflix 另行公佈。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BB14B6DB-A69D-4A48-BD94-2710A420CE5B.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9AE31C7E-A16E-4556-B99B-94E316367945-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9AE31C7E-A16E-4556-B99B-94E316367945-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9AE31C7E-A16E-4556-B99B-94E316367945-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9AE31C7E-A16E-4556-B99B-94E316367945.jpeg 990w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">首批推出的 5 款遊戲包括《Stranger Things: 1984（BonusXP）》、《Stranger Things 3: The Game（BonusXP）》、《Shooting Hoops（Frosty Pop）》、《Card Blast（Amuzo &amp; Rogue Games）》和《Teeter Up（Frosty Pop）》，任何 Netflix 訂閱用戶均可免費玩 Netflix Games 遊戲，遊戲服務細節可在官網查閱。據 Netflix 表示，Netflix Games 從今天起就會陸續推送給超過 190 個國家地區，在美國已經投入服務，至於香港應需要再等一段時間；遊戲語言目前也只支援英文，尚未提供中文。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63803"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fXrgqkbllso?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#03