400;">近日國泰推出「模擬飛行 staycation 」套餐，讓客人體驗模擬駕駛艙飛行。參加者可以到國泰城的模擬駕駛艙，體驗 45 分鐘模擬飛行之旅，更可選擇「飛」往杜</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">拜、紐約或東京等地，客人還可選擇在可同氣候環境下，享受這次飛行旅程。是次的「飛行」活動可讓參加者一嘗成為機師的滋味，更安排了 15 分鐘時間向客人提供攝影服務，留下難忘回憶。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069393" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/71B0BAEA-D1E7-4CDD-BF88-42C7C76B09A4-694x347.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/71B0BAEA-D1E7-4CDD-BF88-42C7C76B09A4-694x347.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/71B0BAEA-D1E7-4CDD-BF88-42C7C76B09A4-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/71B0BAEA-D1E7-4CDD-BF88-42C7C76B09A4.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069394 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5EEADEDE-10E2-4BDC-94A9-F8F546BE8588.jpeg" alt="" width="450" height="450" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5EEADEDE-10E2-4BDC-94A9-F8F546BE8588.jpeg 450w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5EEADEDE-10E2-4BDC-94A9-F8F546BE8588-120x120.jpeg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 450px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">除模擬飛行外，套餐中還包括了奕居「Studio 70 城景客房」或「海景套房」3 日 2 夜連早餐，更會提供轎車接送由國泰城到酒店。在完成整個 staycation 之旅後，可獲得波音 777-200 客機原材料改造而成的行李掛牌等禮物。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CE626D31-27D6-48E6-BA78-230CBA77CEE6-694x347.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CE626D31-27D6-48E6-BA78-230CBA77CEE6-694x347.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CE626D31-27D6-48E6-BA78-230CBA77CEE6-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CE626D31-27D6-48E6-BA78-230CBA77CEE6.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Staycation 套餐僅於 11 月及 12 月限時推出，並於 11 月 4 日起接受預訂。「城景客房」3 日 2 夜二人套票價為 HK$25,190.11；「海景套房」二人套票價則為 HK$30,690.13。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.cathaypacific.com/cx/zh_HK/offers/flight-simulator-the-upper-house-staycation.html?utm_source=FACEBOOK&amp;utm_medium=SOCIAL-HK-GBL&amp;utm_campaign=20211102-CX-HK-FLTSIMSTAYCATION&amp;utm_content=PAID">國泰航空</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwireh</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
